          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2329-Step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2329-Step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> and <strong>halved beans</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until slightly softened</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2329-Step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2329-Step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2329-Step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2329-Step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2329-Step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your<strong> halloumi</strong> into thin strips (save the <strong>halloumi liquid</strong> from the packet for later!)</p><p>Heat a separate large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced halloumi</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min on each side or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2329-Step-4-x200.jpg",
