            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> and shake off the excess water</p><p>Squeeze your pouch[es] of <strong>cooked brown long grain rice </strong>to separate the grains</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
