            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>spinach </strong>to the pan with your <strong>chopped dates</strong>,<strong> cooked brown long grain rice</strong>,<strong> halloumi liquid </strong>and a small splash of <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Stir it altogether and cook, covered, for 3-4 min or until warmed through and the spinach has wilted – this is your <strong>fruity spinach pilaf</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2329-Step-7-x200.jpg",
