      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> fruity spinach pilaf</strong> topped with the <strong>halloumi slices</strong></p><p>Drizzle your<strong> natural yoghurt</strong> over the top and season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
